{"tid":1403584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【GFRIEND香港演唱會】SinB負傷上陣　Yuju三段高音震撼現場","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:23:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd7556c2607b3f5cff7820d4eedde7b1b879688","tid":1403584,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女團GFRIEND今天（3日）在香港舉行演唱會「2019 GFRIEND ASIA TOUR [GOGOGFRIEND!] in HONG KONG」，6位成員Sowon、Sinb、Eunha、Yuju、Yerin和Umji相隔約一年再訪港，同樣吸引了大量Bubby（GFRIEND粉絲）入場支持，現場非常熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n穿着七彩打歌服的GFRIEND在舞台中央登場，以大熱曲《Me Gustas Tu》、《LIFE IS A PARTY》和《Vacation》掀開演唱會序章，可是主舞擔當的SinB卻因膊頭有傷，一輪綵排後始終未能一同參與激烈的舞蹈，略為可惜。SinB就先與香港粉絲道歉，她講到：「本來想帶給大家帥氣的表演，可是未能做到非常抱歉。我答應大家會左邊又坐下，右邊又坐下，前面又坐下，一邊坐着為成員打氣，一邊與大家交流。」而相隔一年沒有來到香港，成員都大讚香港粉絲非常熱情，又賣口乖話「好掛住你哋」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117902/org/47f4d2e299768ad54ab15941b292ed43.JPG/uLACLGfbPtcgfay4NIF7BoKGZM99y7gWB2EP5i1hD-Y?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117902%2Forg%2F47f4d2e299768ad54ab15941b292ed43.JPG%2FuLACLGfbPtcgfay4NIF7BoKGZM99y7gWB2EP5i1hD-Y%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0cb05b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGFRIEND相隔約一年，今天再在香港開演唱會。（陳志嵐攝）<br />\n<br />\n唱出一連串歌曲又大展刀群舞的GFRIEND，不停大讚香港粉絲非常熱情，令她們也感受到現場非常「熱」。為了與香港粉絲更直接溝通，Yuju又用英文向現場觀眾問問題。當中6人答謝香港Buddy讓她們願望成真再回香港開演唱會，而她們也實現了粉絲想與GFRIEND見面的願望。隊長Sowon又特別學了一句廣東話，對香港粉絲說：「願望成真！」可見6人渴望與大家直接溝通的心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117876/org/ecb52f16b57ffd65c7036f728beede3a.JPG/TCjP7ZggwGV7gPuF0dqPZ2pEzI1cRiRcg23_p6lt_6c?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117876%2Forg%2Fecb52f16b57ffd65c7036f728beede3a.JPG%2FTCjP7ZggwGV7gPuF0dqPZ2pEzI1cRiRcg23_p6lt_6c%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=fa437f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117891/org/16d61fcc4f164fecbebf6150d2c4b95c.JPG/v17sUu5j1pHiHFKELH4loxE5PwpfucuJUKjobXqo6G0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117891%2Forg%2F16d61fcc4f164fecbebf6150d2c4b95c.JPG%2Fv17sUu5j1pHiHFKELH4loxE5PwpfucuJUKjobXqo6G0&h=656fc78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117900/org/06f48f76889615d0b6f2c616ab9dae83.JPG/7Kr8XZGQZWWk1bw2Jxfa1idAeXAyLMWRObidtBO4nbQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117900%2Forg%2F06f48f76889615d0b6f2c616ab9dae83.JPG%2F7Kr8XZGQZWWk1bw2Jxfa1idAeXAyLMWRObidtBO4nbQ&h=cedd7edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117888/org/cdce5f357d59e8bd1b5ae5b7823d82ee.JPG/lMScYgKsXiMCPQLRKLpRHPH2r3fTD4FWhGWvg65lr4M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117888%2Forg%2Fcdce5f357d59e8bd1b5ae5b7823d82ee.JPG%2FlMScYgKsXiMCPQLRKLpRHPH2r3fTD4FWhGWvg65lr4M&h=a4372ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117894/org/81bea58402c268e0f3d22a49a6a83495.JPG/u_ZeHqVhXLlTHCItXjhr6djhvpt_anj2g_H8Kqnx_Co\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117894%2Forg%2F81bea58402c268e0f3d22a49a6a83495.JPG%2Fu_ZeHqVhXLlTHCItXjhr6djhvpt_anj2g_H8Kqnx_Co&h=853777a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3117893/org/c0617d7214ab1de6deeb7cd7725208b0.JPG/SYQC3qLEZx--49YULLimxqGVLE7Bhqa_8P4RFdb-ERU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3117893%2Forg%2Fc0617d7214ab1de6deeb7cd7725208b0.JPG%2FSYQC3qLEZx--49YULLimxqGVLE7Bhqa_8P4RFdb-ERU&h=24b5ba8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e11298cbe8bdb6dbd88fe08dd1480a5784647f8c","tid":1403584,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a4a21a57b5b22d06c91949a1170dda926ff7bc","tid":1403